<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {$_ENV['APP_NAME']}</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #2d3561, #4a569d, #5f4d93, #8b5cf6);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradient 15s ease infinite;
            color: #2c3e50;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        @keyframes gradient {
            0% { background-position: 0 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0 50%; }
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 4rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }
        .status {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .status-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .status-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #28a745;
        }
        .footer {
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #adb5bd;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>ðŸŽ¯ {$_ENV['APP_NAME']}</h1>
    <p>Welcome to your new Symfony application.</p>
    <div class="status">
        <div class="status-item">
            <span class="status-dot"></span>
            <span>Application Ready</span>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
            <span class="status-dot"></span>
            <span>Services Active</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Built with Symfony Framework</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>